          },
          "datePublished": "2023-03-10",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Wonderful school. A home away from\nHome for my child. He is so well looked after by the entire staff and I have seen such a big developmental leap in his knowledge about the world and his social skills since he has started playful minds.\nIt is heartwarming to see even the owner and principal greet him by his name in every interaction.\nShruti ma’am-the principal- even took him under her wing when he had first started going without me to school. He used to sit in her room and play with her.\nI have seen her do this with other kids during their transition time too. Amazing!\nPersonal attention is to the T!\nOther commercial schools with 20-30 kids in a class will never give this kind of attention.\nHappy to be here! So Happy my child goes here!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Playful Minds - Sector 26A"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "nimisha goel"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-03-09",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "If I could go back in time and attend Playschool I would go to Playful Minds. I am actually jealous of my son for having the best possible play school experience there could be. Playful minds provides a safe haven for all these little babies. My son has been going here since he was 2.5 and now he’s graduating at 4 years old to big school. I am amazed on a daily basis by the things he learns at this little age and the way he has grown in terms of his confidence and knowledge. A special mention for the cleanliness, attention to detail and the planning with which the curriculum is structured. Each and every staff member from the most senior to the ground level takes complete care of the children. I leave my kid here worry free every day, which is the best compliment a parent can give.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
