          },
          "datePublished": "2023-02-28",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It is a wonderful school. The teachers are really dedicated and great with children. The school not only focuses on academics but also on the overall development of the child. The children are taken out for excursions where the teachers and the staff take utmost care of the safety and comfort of the children. The activities events and summer camps held in school are awesome. I have seen a remarkable development in my daughter. The school family is very warm and approachable my daughter has a huge smile every day going to school and excited to meet her teachers. I big shout out to Sonali Ma'am Shruti Ma'am Eesha Ma'am Shivani Ma'am and all the other teachers and staff for taking such good care of our children we know they are in safe hands. It is a lovely experience to be a part of this school (family) 🤗",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
