          "reviewBody": "One of the best play schools in the locality. We have been sending our kid for the last 1 year and we are impressed with the pedagogy. We have seen our child develop holistically over the last few months.\nThe teachers are awesome, batch size is small, focus on individual child. Nothing more than you can ask for.",
